          "activation_name": "Mesmerizing Lights",
          "effect": "All creatures within the bright light of the anglerfish lantern must succeed at a DC 19 Will save or be fascinated by the light for 1 round (1 minute on a critical failure). The fascination ends if the light is extinguished. Aquatic animals and creatures with the water trait take a \u20132 circumstance penalty to this check. Regardless of the result, the creature then becomes immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.",
